SPOLJARIC HAPPY, BACK IN GROOVE WITH TORONTO 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times NewfYMIvice clients.)  
 By DAN RALEY  
 c.1999 Seattle Post-Intelligencer  
<TEXT>
<P>
   TORONTO _ For nearly half an hour Wednesday, Paul Spoljaric sat
in front of his Blue Jays clubhouse cubicle, signing a huge staci &UR;
</P>
</TEXT>
