   NATIONAL NEWS (``a'' category)
</P>
<P>
   QUAKE-PREDICTION (San Francisco) _ Earthquake forecasters
apparently predicted Tuesday's devastating earthquake in Turkey two
years in advance. Conceivably, the forecast _ published in a
scientific journal in 1997 _ might have been just a lucky guess.
Still, if it was a guess, it was a remarkably good one. By KEAY
