completing its $19 million purchase of Fresh Juice Co. Inc.,
Saratoga Beverage Group Inc. is ready to roll out a product that's
meant to blend the best of both companies: Fresh-squeezed juice in
a bottle. The product combines the New Jersey company's strength _
fresh-squeezed juices _ with Saratoga Beverage's expertise in
marketing bottled products. By CLAIRE HUGHES
</P>
