Turturro's weirdo turn of the century tale of a playwright. Grade:
B-. (Longino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIES-TINGLE _ Movie review of ``Teaching Mrs. Tingle.'' Kevin
Williamson (Hollywood's Mr. ``Scream'') is writer/director of this
schizoid high school movie about a trio of teens who hold their
devilish history teacher (Helen Mirren) hostage. The film can't
seem to find its groove. Is it a horror flick? A nasty-nice Disney
flick in disguise? One thing it's got for sure is a very grown-up
sex scene between young stars from ``Dawson's Creek'' and ``Seventh
Heaven.'' Grade: C-. (Longino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 11.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIES-TRICK _ Movie review: ``Trick.'' A gay story of simple
lust that turns into a simple love story. Grade: B. (Ringel,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
