Lou Gehrig, baseball, 1992 &QL; 
Ken Griffey Jr., baseball, 1996 &QL; 
Franco Harris, football, 1997 &QL; 
Doug Heir, wheelchair track and field, 1986 &QL; 
Jim Hershberger, track and field, 1986 &QL; 
Peter Jacobsen, golf, 1996 &QL; 
Bruce Jenner, track and field, 1976 &QL; 
