   WHY INDEPENDENT EVANGELICAL CHURCHES ARE GROWING, by Mike
McManus
</P>
<P>
   Last May I visited Harvest Fellowship Community Church in San
Antonio. I immediately saw why independent evangelical churches
like this are booming across America, while many traditional
liturgical churches are slowly eroding down to a loyal band of the
white-haired, bald and stooped.
