<P>
   &QR;  Asheville, N.C. _ Biltmore Estate's Summer Evenings Concerts
on the South Terrace overlooking the Blue Ridge Mountains features
jazz artists Spyro Gyra and guitarist Earl Klugh (Saturday); and
the big band sounds of the Tommy Dorsey Orchestra (Aug. 28). By
reservation only; $35. 1-800-323-6804.
