<P>
   BBN-BRAVES-HALL _ ATLANTA _ Seldom can baseball franchises boast
of four Hall of Fame players, who so defined the identity of the
franchise. But that's the case with Hank Aaron, Warren Spahn, Phil
Niekro and Eddie Mathews, the first class to be inducted in the
Braves Hall of Fame. Ceremony is today. (Stinson, Atlanta
