   WITH
</P>
<P>
   WINSTON CUP NOTES _ Breaking up is hard to do, but it appears
inevitable with Jeff Gordon and crew chief Ray Evernham. (Carvell,
Atlanta-Journal Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   RACE AT A GLANCE _ A look at Sunday's Pepsi 400 at Michigan
International.
</P>
<P>
   BUSCH SERIES NOTES _ The AllCar Motorsports and Air Jamaica
Vacations Chevy team finally is returning to the Busch Series after
two months of preparation and will compete in all remaining races.
(Carvell, Atlanta-Journal Constitution)
</P>
