   HILLARY-TEXAS (Houston) _ First Lady Hillary Rodham Clinton
swings through Texas on a private fund-raising tour and finds the
Lone Star State receptive. The presumptive Democratic candidate for
Senate in New York raised more than $500,00 _ $150,000 of which
came from a small dinner party in the River Oaks section of
Houston. By SHELBY HODGES.
</P>
